{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":285,"text":"Throughout my career, I've been fortunate enough"},{"time":3360,"text":"to work with many of the great"},{"time":4719,"text":"international architects,"},{"time":6445,"text":"documenting their work and observing"},{"time":8869,"text":"how their designs have the capacity"},{"time":10828,"text":"to influence the cities in which they sit."},{"time":13797,"text":"I think of new cities like Dubai"},{"time":16640,"text":"or ancient cities like Rome"},{"time":19117,"text":"with Zaha Hadid's incredible MAXXI museum,"},{"time":22479,"text":"or like right here in New York with the High Line,"},{"time":25296,"text":"a city which has been so much influenced"},{"time":27867,"text":"by the development of this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29570,"text":"But what I find really fascinating"},{"time":31645,"text":"is what happens when architects and planners leave"},{"time":34741,"text":"and these places become appropriated by people,"},{"time":37860,"text":"like here in Chandigarh, India,"},{"time":40200,"text":"the city which has been completely designed"},{"time":42520,"text":"by the architect Le Corbusier."},{"time":44659,"text":"Now 60 years later, the city has been taken over"},{"time":47639,"text":"by people in very different ways"},{"time":49260,"text":"from whatever perhaps intended for,"},{"time":52582,"text":"like here, where you have the people"},{"time":54888,"text":"sitting in the windows of the assembly hall."},{"time":57851,"text":"But over the course of several years,"},{"time":59938,"text":"I've been documenting Rem Koolhaas's"},{"time":62356,"text":"CCTV building in Beijing"},{"time":64402,"text":"and the olympic stadium in the same city"},{"time":67240,"text":"by the architects Herzog and de Meuron."},{"time":70384,"text":"At these large-scale construction sites in China,"},{"time":73829,"text":"you see a sort of makeshift camp"},{"time":75952,"text":"where workers live during the entire building process."},{"time":80142,"text":"As the length of the construction takes years,"},{"time":82624,"text":"workers end up forming a rather rough-and-ready"},{"time":85382,"text":"informal city, making for quite a juxtaposition"},{"time":88648,"text":"against the sophisticated structures that they're building."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92091,"text":"Over the past seven years, I've been following"},{"time":94300,"text":"my fascination with the built environment,"},{"time":96971,"text":"and for those of you who know me, you would say"},{"time":99674,"text":"that this obsession has led me to live"},{"time":101660,"text":"out of a suitcase 365 days a year."},{"time":105082,"text":"Being constantly on the move"},{"time":107579,"text":"means that sometimes I am able"},{"time":109394,"text":"to catch life's most unpredictable moments,"},{"time":112570,"text":"like here in New York"},{"time":114551,"text":"the day after the Sandy storm hit the city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118944,"text":"Just over three years ago,"},{"time":121008,"text":"I was for the first time in Caracas, Venezuela,"},{"time":123694,"text":"and while flying over the city, I was just amazed"},{"time":126490,"text":"by the extent to which the slums"},{"time":128530,"text":"reach into every corner of the city,"},{"time":130979,"text":"a place where nearly 70 percent of the population"},{"time":133716,"text":"lives in slums,"},{"time":135057,"text":"draped literally all over the mountains."},{"time":138350,"text":"During a conversation with local architects Urban-Think Tank,"},{"time":141777,"text":"I learned about the Torre David,"},{"time":144130,"text":"a 45-story office building which sits"},{"time":146673,"text":"right in the center of Caracas."},{"time":148726,"text":"The building was under construction"},{"time":150329,"text":"until the collapse of the Venezuelan economy"},{"time":152855,"text":"and the death of the developer in the early '90s."},{"time":156221,"text":"About eight years ago, people started moving"},{"time":159183,"text":"into the abandoned tower"},{"time":161196,"text":"and began to build their homes right in between"},{"time":163215,"text":"every column of this unfinished tower."},{"time":166414,"text":"There's only one little entrance to the entire building,"},{"time":169211,"text":"and the 3,000 residents come in and out"},{"time":172149,"text":"through that single door."},{"time":174217,"text":"Together, the inhabitants created public spaces"},{"time":177106,"text":"and designed them to feel more like a home"},{"time":179379,"text":"and less like an unfinished tower."},{"time":181974,"text":"In the lobby, they painted the walls and planted trees."},{"time":185489,"text":"They also made a basketball court."},{"time":188499,"text":"But when you look up closely,"},{"time":190199,"text":"you see massive holes where elevators"},{"time":192680,"text":"and services would have run through."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195260,"text":"Within the tower, people have come up"},{"time":197249,"text":"with all sorts of solutions"},{"time":199515,"text":"in response to the various needs"},{"time":201496,"text":"which arise from living in an unfinished tower."},{"time":204983,"text":"With no elevators,"},{"time":206182,"text":"the tower is like a 45-story walkup."},{"time":209510,"text":"Designed in very specific ways"},{"time":211760,"text":"by this group of people"},{"time":213236,"text":"who haven't had any education in architecture or design."},{"time":217132,"text":"And with each inhabitant finding their own"},{"time":219413,"text":"unique way of coming by,"},{"time":221380,"text":"this tower becomes like a living city,"},{"time":224182,"text":"a place which is alive with micro-economies"},{"time":227394,"text":"and small businesses."},{"time":229311,"text":"The inventive inhabitants, for instance,"},{"time":231925,"text":"find opportunities in the most unexpected cases,"},{"time":234656,"text":"like the adjacent parking garage,"},{"time":236781,"text":"which has been reclaimed as a taxi route"},{"time":238858,"text":"to shuttle the inhabitants up through the ramps"},{"time":241156,"text":"in order to shorten the hike"},{"time":242603,"text":"up to the apartments."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246621,"text":"A walk through the tower"},{"time":248531,"text":"reveals how residents have figured out"},{"time":250641,"text":"how to create walls, how to make an air flow,"},{"time":254167,"text":"how to create transparency,"},{"time":256130,"text":"circulation throughout the tower,"},{"time":258554,"text":"essentially creating a home"},{"time":260373,"text":"that's completely adapted"},{"time":262021,"text":"to the conditions of the site."},{"time":265299,"text":"When a new inhabitant moves into the tower,"},{"time":267424,"text":"they already have a roof over their head,"},{"time":269332,"text":"so they just typically mark their space"},{"time":271371,"text":"with a few curtains or sheets."},{"time":274287,"text":"Slowly, from found materials, walls rise,"},{"time":277459,"text":"and people create a space out of any found objects"},{"time":280382,"text":"or materials."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282271,"text":"It's remarkable to see the design decisions"},{"time":284771,"text":"that they're making,"},{"time":286447,"text":"like when everything is made out of red bricks,"},{"time":289082,"text":"some residents will cover that red brick"},{"time":291347,"text":"with another layer of red brick-patterned wallpaper"},{"time":295208,"text":"just to make it a kind of clean finish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300260,"text":"The inhabitants literally built up these homes"},{"time":302719,"text":"with their own hands, and this labor of love"},{"time":304876,"text":"instills a great sense of pride"},{"time":306629,"text":"in many families living in this tower."},{"time":309881,"text":"They typically make the best out of their conditions,"},{"time":312815,"text":"and try to make their spaces look nice and homey,"},{"time":315623,"text":"or at least up until as far as they can reach."},{"time":319170,"text":"Throughout the tower, you come across"},{"time":322182,"text":"all kinds of services, like the barber,"},{"time":324348,"text":"small factories, and every floor has"},{"time":328161,"text":"a little grocery store or shop."},{"time":331585,"text":"And you even find a church."},{"time":334095,"text":"And on the 30th floor, there is a gym"},{"time":336459,"text":"where all the weights and barbells"},{"time":338213,"text":"are made out of the leftover pulleys"},{"time":340009,"text":"from the elevators which were never installed."},{"time":343419,"text":"From the outside, behind this always-changing facade,"},{"time":346054,"text":"you see how the fixed concrete beams"},{"time":347673,"text":"provide a framework for the inhabitants"},{"time":349538,"text":"to create their homes"},{"time":351005,"text":"in an organic, intuitive way"},{"time":352881,"text":"that responds directly to their needs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":355598,"text":"Let's go now to Africa, to Nigeria,"},{"time":358253,"text":"to a community called Makoko,"},{"time":360824,"text":"a slum where 150,000 people"},{"time":363383,"text":"live just meters above the Lagos Lagoon."},{"time":366565,"text":"While it may appear to be a completely chaotic place,"},{"time":370279,"text":"when you see it from above, there seems to be"},{"time":372685,"text":"a whole grid of waterways and canals"},{"time":375850,"text":"connecting each and every home."},{"time":378364,"text":"From the main dock, people board long wooden canoes"},{"time":382578,"text":"which carry them out to their various homes and shops"},{"time":385248,"text":"located in the expansive area."},{"time":387923,"text":"When out on the water, it's clear"},{"time":389870,"text":"that life has been completely adapted"},{"time":391759,"text":"to this very specific way of living."},{"time":394398,"text":"Even the canoes become variety stores"},{"time":397045,"text":"where ladies paddle from house to house,"},{"time":398985,"text":"selling anything from toothpaste to fresh fruits."},{"time":403101,"text":"Behind every window and door frame,"},{"time":405120,"text":"you'll see a small child peering back at you,"},{"time":407823,"text":"and while Makoko seems to be packed with people,"},{"time":410807,"text":"what's more shocking is actually"},{"time":412642,"text":"the amount of children pouring out of every building."},{"time":416127,"text":"The population growth in Nigeria,"},{"time":418107,"text":"and especially in these areas like Makoko,"},{"time":420576,"text":"are painful reminders"},{"time":422728,"text":"of how out of control things really are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":426967,"text":"In Makoko, very few systems"},{"time":429246,"text":"and infrastructures exist."},{"time":431112,"text":"Electricity is rigged and freshest water"},{"time":434044,"text":"comes from self-built wells throughout the area."},{"time":437409,"text":"This entire economic model"},{"time":439813,"text":"is designed to meet a specific way of living"},{"time":442605,"text":"on the water, so fishing and boat-making"},{"time":445720,"text":"are common professions."},{"time":447495,"text":"You'll have a set of entrepreneurs"},{"time":449462,"text":"who have set up businesses throughout the area,"},{"time":452486,"text":"like barbershops, CD and DVD stores,"},{"time":457286,"text":"movie theaters, tailors, everything is there."},{"time":462649,"text":"There is even a photo studio"},{"time":464444,"text":"where you see the sort of aspiration"},{"time":466201,"text":"to live in a real house or to be associated"},{"time":469501,"text":"with a faraway place, like that hotel in Sweden."}]},{"cues":[{"time":473800,"text":"On this particular evening,"},{"time":475424,"text":"I came across this live band"},{"time":477528,"text":"dressed to the T in their coordinating outfits."},{"time":480679,"text":"They were floating through the canals"},{"time":482709,"text":"in a large canoe with a fitted-out generator"},{"time":485633,"text":"for all of the community to enjoy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":489969,"text":"By nightfall, the area becomes almost pitch black,"},{"time":492960,"text":"save for a small lightbulb"},{"time":494788,"text":"or a fire."}]},{"cues":[{"time":497522,"text":"What originally brought me to Makoko"},{"time":500137,"text":"was this project from a friend of mine,"},{"time":501944,"text":"Kunl√© Adeyemi, who recently finished building"},{"time":504745,"text":"this three-story floating school"},{"time":506791,"text":"for the kids in Makoko."},{"time":508812,"text":"With this entire village existing on the water,"},{"time":511841,"text":"public space is very limited,"},{"time":514264,"text":"so now that the school is finished,"},{"time":515928,"text":"the ground floor is a playground for the kids,"},{"time":519302,"text":"but when classes are out, the platform"},{"time":521169,"text":"is just like a town square,"},{"time":522740,"text":"where the fishermen mend their nets"},{"time":525135,"text":"and floating shopkeepers dock their boats."}]},{"cues":[{"time":529300,"text":"Another place I'd like to share with you"},{"time":531830,"text":"is the Zabbaleen in Cairo."},{"time":533878,"text":"They're descendants of farmers who began migrating"},{"time":536637,"text":"from the upper Egypt in the '40s,"},{"time":539107,"text":"and today they make their living"},{"time":540533,"text":"by collecting and recycling waste from homes"},{"time":543723,"text":"from all over Cairo."},{"time":545974,"text":"For years, the Zabbaleen would live in makeshift villages"},{"time":549096,"text":"where they would move around"},{"time":550765,"text":"trying to avoid the local authorities,"},{"time":553284,"text":"but in the early 1980s, they settled"},{"time":555603,"text":"on the Mokattam rocks"},{"time":557320,"text":"just at the eastern edge of the city."},{"time":559969,"text":"Today, they live in this area,"},{"time":562000,"text":"approximately 50,000 to 70,000 people,"},{"time":564804,"text":"who live in this community of self-built"},{"time":566937,"text":"multi-story houses"},{"time":569117,"text":"where up to three generations live in one structure."},{"time":573410,"text":"While these apartments that they built for themselves"},{"time":575888,"text":"appear to lack any planning or formal grid,"},{"time":578873,"text":"each family specializing in a certain form of recycling"},{"time":582279,"text":"means that the ground floor of each apartment"},{"time":584512,"text":"is reserved for garbage-related activities"},{"time":588169,"text":"and the upper floor is dedicated to living space."},{"time":592192,"text":"I find it incredible to see"},{"time":594063,"text":"how these piles and piles of garbage"},{"time":595999,"text":"are invisible to the people who live there,"},{"time":598510,"text":"like this very distinguished man who is posing"},{"time":601910,"text":"while all this garbage is sort of streaming out behind him,"},{"time":606119,"text":"or like these two young men who are sitting"},{"time":608759,"text":"and chatting amongst these tons of garbage."},{"time":613611,"text":"While to most of us, living amongst"},{"time":615344,"text":"these piles and piles of garbage"},{"time":617432,"text":"may seem totally uninhabitable,"},{"time":619783,"text":"to those in the Zabbaleen, this is just"},{"time":621873,"text":"a different type of normal."},{"time":624352,"text":"In all these places I've talked about today,"},{"time":626989,"text":"what I do find fascinating is that there's really"},{"time":629110,"text":"no such thing as normal,"},{"time":630708,"text":"and it proves that people are able to adapt"},{"time":632913,"text":"to any kind of situation."},{"time":635288,"text":"Throughout the day, it's quite common"},{"time":636804,"text":"to come across a small party taking place"},{"time":640152,"text":"in the streets, just like this engagement party."},{"time":643996,"text":"In this tradition, the bride-to-be"},{"time":645983,"text":"displays all of their belongings,"},{"time":648128,"text":"which they soon bring to their new husband."},{"time":650322,"text":"A gathering like this one"},{"time":652353,"text":"offers such a juxtaposition"},{"time":654250,"text":"where all the new stuff is displayed"},{"time":657028,"text":"and all the garbage is used"},{"time":659394,"text":"as props to display all their new home accessories."},{"time":666031,"text":"Like Makoko and the Torre David,"},{"time":668197,"text":"throughout the Zabbaleen you'll find all"},{"time":669742,"text":"the same facilities as in any typical neighborhood."},{"time":672886,"text":"There are the retail shops, the cafes"},{"time":674966,"text":"and the restaurants, and the community"},{"time":677286,"text":"is this community of Coptic Christians,"},{"time":680227,"text":"so you'll also find a church,"},{"time":682466,"text":"along with the scores of religious iconographies"},{"time":685911,"text":"throughout the area,"},{"time":687669,"text":"and also all the everyday services"},{"time":690858,"text":"like the electronic repair shops,"},{"time":692657,"text":"the barbers, everything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":695745,"text":"Visiting the homes of the Zabbaleen"},{"time":697918,"text":"is also full of surprises."},{"time":699607,"text":"While from the outside,"},{"time":701119,"text":"these homes look like any other informal structure"},{"time":703662,"text":"in the city, when you step inside,"},{"time":705980,"text":"you are met with all manner of design decisions"},{"time":709843,"text":"and interior decoration."},{"time":712110,"text":"Despite having limited access to space and money,"},{"time":715274,"text":"the homes in the area are designed"},{"time":717153,"text":"with care and detail."},{"time":719139,"text":"Every apartment is unique,"},{"time":721182,"text":"and this individuality tells a story"},{"time":722975,"text":"about each family's circumstances and values."},{"time":726101,"text":"Many of these people take their homes"},{"time":728247,"text":"and interior spaces very seriously,"},{"time":731415,"text":"putting a lot of work and care"},{"time":732922,"text":"into the details."},{"time":734248,"text":"The shared spaces are also treated in the same manner,"},{"time":737421,"text":"where walls are decorated in faux marble patterns."}]},{"cues":[{"time":741278,"text":"But despite this elaborate decor,"},{"time":744261,"text":"sometimes these apartments are used"},{"time":746815,"text":"in very unexpected ways,"},{"time":748625,"text":"like this home which caught my attention"},{"time":751005,"text":"while all the mud and the grass was literally"},{"time":754487,"text":"seeping out under the front door."},{"time":756974,"text":"When I was let in, it appeared that this fifth-floor apartment"},{"time":760773,"text":"was being transformed into a complete animal farm,"},{"time":764081,"text":"where six or seven cows stood grazing"},{"time":766972,"text":"in what otherwise would be the living room."},{"time":771644,"text":"But then in the apartment across the hall"},{"time":775012,"text":"from this cow shed lives a newly married couple"},{"time":777535,"text":"in what locals describe"},{"time":779361,"text":"as one of the nicest apartments in the area."}]},{"cues":[{"time":787482,"text":"The attention to this detail astonished me,"},{"time":790708,"text":"and as the owner of the home so proudly"},{"time":793379,"text":"led me around this apartment,"},{"time":795365,"text":"from floor to ceiling, every part was decorated."},{"time":799081,"text":"But if it weren't for the strangely familiar"},{"time":802883,"text":"stomach-churning odor that constantly"},{"time":805746,"text":"passes through the apartment,"},{"time":809191,"text":"it would be easy to forget"},{"time":811784,"text":"that you are standing next to a cow shed"},{"time":814476,"text":"and on top of a landfill."},{"time":819973,"text":"What moved me the most was that despite"},{"time":822652,"text":"these seemingly inhospitable conditions,"},{"time":824686,"text":"I was welcomed with open arms"},{"time":826479,"text":"into a home that was made with love, care,"},{"time":830405,"text":"and unreserved passion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":832655,"text":"Let's move across the map to China,"},{"time":836039,"text":"to an area called Shanxi, Henan and Gansu."},{"time":839926,"text":"In a region famous for the soft, porous Loess Plateau soil,"},{"time":843616,"text":"there lived until recently an estimated"},{"time":846299,"text":"40 million people in these houses underground."},{"time":850168,"text":"These dwellings are called the yaodongs."},{"time":852619,"text":"Through this architecture by subtraction,"},{"time":854809,"text":"these yaodongs are built literally inside of the soil."},{"time":858396,"text":"In these villages, you see an entirely altered landscape,"},{"time":862270,"text":"and hidden behind these mounds of dirt"},{"time":865016,"text":"are these square, rectangular houses"},{"time":867516,"text":"which sit seven meters below the ground."},{"time":870107,"text":"When I asked people why they were digging"},{"time":872095,"text":"their houses from the ground,"},{"time":873984,"text":"they simply replied that they are poor wheat"},{"time":876007,"text":"and apple farmers who didn't have the money"},{"time":878187,"text":"to buy materials, and this digging out"},{"time":881588,"text":"was their most logical form of living."}]},{"cues":[{"time":886056,"text":"From Makoko to Zabbaleen, these communities"},{"time":888954,"text":"have approached the tasks of planning,"},{"time":890953,"text":"design and management of their communities"},{"time":893352,"text":"and neighborhoods in ways that respond"},{"time":895731,"text":"specifically to their environment and circumstances."},{"time":899641,"text":"Created by these very people who live,"},{"time":901872,"text":"work and play in these particular spaces,"},{"time":905583,"text":"these neighborhoods are intuitively designed"},{"time":908580,"text":"to make the most of their circumstances."},{"time":911618,"text":"In most of these places, the government"},{"time":913523,"text":"is completely absent, leaving inhabitants"},{"time":916052,"text":"with no choice but to reappropriate found materials,"},{"time":919971,"text":"and while these communities are highly disadvantaged,"},{"time":922943,"text":"they do present examples"},{"time":924985,"text":"of brilliant forms of ingenuity,"},{"time":927433,"text":"and prove that indeed we have the ability"},{"time":929761,"text":"to adapt to all manner of circumstances."},{"time":933304,"text":"What makes places like the Torre David"},{"time":935497,"text":"particularly remarkable"},{"time":937294,"text":"is this sort of skeleton framework"},{"time":939195,"text":"where people can have a foundation"},{"time":940817,"text":"where they can tap into."},{"time":942889,"text":"Now imagine what these already ingenious communities"},{"time":945987,"text":"could create themselves,"},{"time":948079,"text":"and how highly particular their solutions would be,"},{"time":950765,"text":"if they were given the basic infrastructures"},{"time":953307,"text":"that they could tap into."}]},{"cues":[{"time":955286,"text":"Today, you see these large residential development projects"},{"time":958793,"text":"which offer cookie-cutter housing solutions"},{"time":961248,"text":"to massive amounts of people."},{"time":963290,"text":"From China to Brazil, these projects attempt"},{"time":965850,"text":"to provide as many houses as possible,"},{"time":968857,"text":"but they're completely generic"},{"time":971060,"text":"and simply do not work as an answer"},{"time":972965,"text":"to the individual needs of the people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":976294,"text":"I would like to end with a quote"},{"time":978748,"text":"from a friend of mine and a source of inspiration,"},{"time":981829,"text":"Zita Cobb, the founder of the wonderful"},{"time":984595,"text":"Shorefast Foundation,"},{"time":986271,"text":"based out of Fogo Island, Newfoundland."},{"time":989360,"text":"She says that \"there's this plague of sameness"},{"time":992201,"text":"which is killing the human joy,\""},{"time":994124,"text":"and I couldn't agree with her more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":996419,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":997862,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}